This font is bundled here so the dashboard can be self-hosted with no Google
Fonts CDN dependency. To refresh: run `./scripts/refresh-fonts.sh`.

Files:
- IBMPlexMono-Regular.woff2 (weight 400)
- IBMPlexMono-Bold.woff2    (weight 700)
